Opens a URL in the player's system browser. The browser will use its existing cookies to determine if the player is logged in, meaning that using this API can result in three differenet cases:

* The player is signed in with the current account
* The player is signed in with a different account
* The player is not signed in at all.

In order to ensure the player is signed in with the same account as the client, leverage Player Platform's [authentication redirect](https://platform.riotgames.com/docs/authenticate-players/how-rso-works/sign-in-on-mobile/authentication-redirect) feature.
